org.codice.ddf.configuration.admin

Class ConfigurationAdminMigration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.codice.ddf.configuration.admin.ConfigurationAdminMigration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ChangeListener, ConfigurationStatusService

    public class ConfigurationAdminMigration
extends Object
implements ChangeListener, ConfigurationStatusService
    Class used to migrate ConfigurationAdmin configurations. This includes importing configuration files from a configuration directory and creating Configuration objects for those and exporting Configuration objects to configuration files.

        failedDirectory - directory where configuration files will be moved when they failed to be processed

    • Method Detail

      • init

        public void init()
          throws IOException
        Loads all the configuration files located in the configuration directory specified in the constructor. Files that have been successfully processed will be moved to the processedDirectory and files that failed to be processed will be moved to the failedDirectory. It will also register for file creation events which will be handled by the notify(Path) method.
        Throws:
        IOException
